{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"My name is Ursus Wehrli, and I would like to talk to you this morning"},{"time":4000,"text":"about my project, Tidying Up Art."},{"time":6000,"text":"First of all -- any questions so far?"},{"time":11000,"text":"First of all, I have to say I'm not from around here."},{"time":14000,"text":"I'm from a completely different cultural area, maybe you noticed?"},{"time":18000,"text":"I mean, I'm wearing a tie, first. And then secondly, I'm a little bit nervous"},{"time":23000,"text":"because I'm speaking in a foreign language,"},{"time":26000,"text":"and I want to apologize in advance, for any mistakes I might make."},{"time":30000,"text":"Because I'm from Switzerland, and I just don't hope you think this is Swiss German"},{"time":35000,"text":"I'm speaking now here. This is just what it sounds like"},{"time":37000,"text":"if we Swiss try to speak American."},{"time":40000,"text":"But don't worry -- I don't have trouble with English, as such."},{"time":43000,"text":"I mean, it's not my problem, it's your language after all."},{"time":47000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":49000,"text":"I am fine. After this presentation here at TED, I can simply go back to Switzerland,"},{"time":53000,"text":"and you have to go on talking like this all the time."},{"time":56000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"So I've been asked by the organizers to read from my book."},{"time":63000,"text":"It's called \"Tidying Up Art\" and it's, as you can see,"},{"time":66000,"text":"it's more or less a picture book."},{"time":69000,"text":"So the reading would be over very quickly."},{"time":73000,"text":"But since I'm here at TED, I decided to hold my talk here in a more modern way,"},{"time":79000,"text":"in the spirit of TED here, and I managed to do some slides here for you."},{"time":83000,"text":"I'd like to show them around so we can just, you know --"},{"time":87000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":89000,"text":"Actually, I managed to prepare for you some enlarged pictures -- even better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"So Tidying Up Art, I mean, I have to say, that's a relatively new term."},{"time":97000,"text":"You won't be familiar with it."},{"time":99000,"text":"I mean, it's a hobby of mine that I've been indulging in for the last few years,"},{"time":104000,"text":"and it all started out with this picture of the American artist, Donald Baechler"},{"time":109000,"text":"I had hanging at home. I had to look at it every day"},{"time":112000,"text":"and after a while I just couldn't stand the mess anymore"},{"time":116000,"text":"this guy was looking at all day long."},{"time":119000,"text":"Yeah, I kind of felt sorry for him."},{"time":122000,"text":"And it seemed to me even he felt really bad"},{"time":124000,"text":"facing these unorganized red squares day after day."},{"time":128000,"text":"So I decided to give him a little support,"},{"time":130000,"text":"and brought some order into neatly stacking the blocks on top of each other."},{"time":135000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":138000,"text":"Yeah. And I think he looks now less miserable."},{"time":142000,"text":"And it was great. With this experience, I started to look more closely"},{"time":148000,"text":"at modern art. Then I realized how, you know, the world of modern art"},{"time":153000,"text":"is particularly topsy-turvy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"And I can show here a very good example."},{"time":158000,"text":"It's actually a simple one, but it's a good one to start with."},{"time":161000,"text":"It's a picture by Paul Klee."},{"time":164000,"text":"And we can see here very clearly, it's a confusion of color."},{"time":168000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":170000,"text":"Yeah. The artist doesn't really seem to know where to put the different colors."},{"time":176000,"text":"The various pictures here of the various elements of the picture --"},{"time":179000,"text":"the whole thing is unstructured."},{"time":180000,"text":"We don't know, maybe Mr. Klee was probably in a hurry, I mean --"},{"time":184000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":186000,"text":"-- maybe he had to catch a plane, or something."},{"time":189000,"text":"We can see here he started out with orange,"},{"time":192000,"text":"and then he already ran out of orange,"},{"time":195000,"text":"and here we can see he decided to take a break for a square."},{"time":199000,"text":"And I would like to show you here my tidied up version of this picture."},{"time":202000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":207000,"text":"We can see now what was barely recognizable in the original:"},{"time":211000,"text":"17 red and orange squares are juxtaposed with just two green squares."},{"time":218000,"text":"Yeah, that's great."},{"time":219000,"text":"So I mean, that's just tidying up for beginners."},{"time":225000,"text":"I would like to show you here a picture which is a bit more advanced."},{"time":228000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":233000,"text":"What can you say? What a mess."},{"time":234000,"text":"I mean, you see, everything seems to have been scattered aimlessly around the space."},{"time":241000,"text":"If my room back home had looked like this,"},{"time":244000,"text":"my mother would have grounded me for three days."},{"time":246000,"text":"So I'd like to -- I wanted to reintroduce some structure into that picture."},{"time":251000,"text":"And that's really advanced tidying up."},{"time":256000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":259000,"text":"Yeah, you're right. Sometimes people clap at this point,"},{"time":261000,"text":"but that's actually more in Switzerland."},{"time":264000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":269000,"text":"We Swiss are famous for chocolate and cheese. Our trains run on time."},{"time":273000,"text":"We are only happy when things are in order."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276000,"text":"But to go on, here is a very good example to see."},{"time":280000,"text":"This is a picture by Joan Miro."},{"time":283000,"text":"And yeah, we can see the artist has drawn a few lines and shapes"},{"time":288000,"text":"and dropped them any old way onto a yellow background."},{"time":292000,"text":"And yeah, it's the sort of thing you produce when you're doodling on the phone."},{"time":295000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":298000,"text":"And this is my --"},{"time":299000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":302000,"text":"-- you can see now the whole thing takes up far less space."},{"time":306000,"text":"It's more economical and also more efficient."},{"time":309000,"text":"With this method Mr. Miro could have saved canvas for another picture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313000,"text":"But I can see in your faces that you're still a little bit skeptical."},{"time":317000,"text":"So that you can just appreciate how serious I am about all this,"},{"time":321000,"text":"I brought along the patents, the specifications for some of these works,"},{"time":326000,"text":"because I've had my working methods patented"},{"time":328000,"text":"at the Eidgenössische Amt für Geistiges Eigentum in Bern, Switzerland."},{"time":332000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":335000,"text":"I'll just quote from the specification."},{"time":337000,"text":"\"Laut den Kunstprüfer Dr. Albrecht --\""},{"time":341000,"text":"It's not finished yet."},{"time":343000,"text":"\"Laut den Kunstprüfer Dr. Albrecht Götz von Ohlenhusen"},{"time":347000,"text":"wird die Verfahrensweise rechtlich geschützt welche die Kunst"},{"time":350000,"text":"durch spezifisch aufgeräumte Regelmässigkeiten"},{"time":352000,"text":"des allgemeinen Formenschatzes"},{"time":354000,"text":"neue Wirkungen zu erzielen möglich wird.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"Ja, well I could have translated that, but you would have been none the wiser."},{"time":363000,"text":"I'm not sure myself what it means but it sounds good anyway."},{"time":367000,"text":"I just realized it's important how one introduces new ideas to people,"},{"time":372000,"text":"that's why these patents are sometimes necessary."},{"time":374000,"text":"I would like to do a short test with you."},{"time":376000,"text":"Everyone is sitting in quite an orderly fashion here this morning."},{"time":379000,"text":"So I would like to ask you all to raise your right hand. Yeah."},{"time":384000,"text":"The right hand is the one we write with, apart from the left-handers."},{"time":387000,"text":"And now, I'll count to three. I mean, it still looks very orderly to me."},{"time":392000,"text":"Now, I'll count to three, and on the count of three"},{"time":394000,"text":"I'd like you all to shake hands with the person behind you. OK?"},{"time":397000,"text":"One, two, three."},{"time":399000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":408000,"text":"You can see now, that's a good example: even behaving in an orderly, systematic way"},{"time":412000,"text":"can sometimes lead to complete chaos."},{"time":415000,"text":"So we can also see that very clearly in this next painting."},{"time":419000,"text":"This is a painting by the artist, Niki de Saint Phalle."},{"time":424000,"text":"And I mean, in the original it's completely unclear to see"},{"time":429000,"text":"what this tangle of colors and shapes is supposed to depict."},{"time":434000,"text":"But in the tidied up version, it's plain to see that it's a sunburnt woman playing volleyball."},{"time":440000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":443000,"text":"Yeah, it's a -- this one here, that's much better."},{"time":450000,"text":"That's a picture by Keith Haring."},{"time":453000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":457000,"text":"I think it doesn't matter."},{"time":459000,"text":"So, I mean, this picture has not even got a proper title."},{"time":463000,"text":"It's called \"Untitled\" and I think that's appropriate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469000,"text":"So, in the tidied-up version we have a sort of Keith Haring spare parts shop."},{"time":474000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":477000,"text":"This is Keith Haring looked at statistically."},{"time":480000,"text":"One can see here quite clearly,"},{"time":482000,"text":"you can see we have 25 pale green elements,"},{"time":486000,"text":"of which one is in the form of a circle."},{"time":488000,"text":"Or here, for example, we have 27 pink squares with only one pink curve."},{"time":493000,"text":"I mean, that's interesting. One could extend this sort of statistical analysis"},{"time":497000,"text":"to cover all Mr. Haring's various works,"},{"time":499000,"text":"in order to establish in which period the artist favored pale green circles or pink squares."},{"time":505000,"text":"And the artist himself could also benefit from this sort of listing procedure"},{"time":509000,"text":"by using it to estimate how many pots of paint he's likely to need in the future."},{"time":514000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515000,"text":"One can obviously also make combinations."},{"time":518000,"text":"For example, with the Keith Haring circles and Kandinsky's dots."},{"time":522000,"text":"You can add them to all the squares of Paul Klee."},{"time":524000,"text":"In the end, one has a list with which one then can arrange."},{"time":527000,"text":"Then you categorize it, then you file it, put that file in a filing cabinet,"},{"time":531000,"text":"put it in your office and you can make a living doing it."},{"time":537000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":539000,"text":"Yeah, from my own experience. So I'm --"},{"time":541000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":544000,"text":"Actually, I mean, here we have some artists that are a bit more structured. It's not too bad."},{"time":549000,"text":"This is Jasper Johns. We can see here he was practicing with his ruler."},{"time":554000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":556000,"text":"But I think it could still benefit from more discipline."},{"time":560000,"text":"And I think the whole thing adds up much better if you do it like this."},{"time":564000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":570000,"text":"And here, that's one of my favorites."},{"time":573000,"text":"Tidying up Rene Magritte -- this is really fun."},{"time":576000,"text":"You know, there is a --"},{"time":577000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":579000,"text":"I'm always being asked what inspired me to embark on all this."},{"time":583000,"text":"It goes back to a time when I was very often staying in hotels."},{"time":586000,"text":"So once I had the opportunity to stay in a ritzy, five-star hotel."},{"time":590000,"text":"And you know, there you had this little sign --"},{"time":592000,"text":"I put this little sign outside the door every morning that read,"},{"time":598000,"text":"\"Please tidy room.\" I don't know if you have them over here."},{"time":601000,"text":"So actually, my room there hasn't been tidied once daily, but three times a day."},{"time":607000,"text":"So after a while I decided to have a little fun,"},{"time":610000,"text":"and before leaving the room each day I'd scatter a few things around the space."},{"time":615000,"text":"Like books, clothes, toothbrush, etc. And it was great."},{"time":619000,"text":"By the time I returned everything had always been neatly returned to its place."},{"time":623000,"text":"But then one morning, I hang the same little sign onto that picture by Vincent van Gogh."},{"time":631000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":633000,"text":"And you have to say this room hadn't been tidied up since 1888."},{"time":639000,"text":"And when I returned it looked like this."},{"time":642000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":649000,"text":"Yeah, at least it is now possible to do some vacuuming."},{"time":651000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":654000,"text":"OK, I mean, I can see there are always people"},{"time":656000,"text":"that like reacting that one or another picture"},{"time":660000,"text":"hasn't been properly tidied up. So we can make a short test with you."},{"time":665000,"text":"This is a picture by Rene Magritte,"},{"time":667000,"text":"and I'd like you all to inwardly -- like in your head, that is --"},{"time":671000,"text":"to tidy that up. So it's possible that some of you would make it like this."},{"time":677000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":679000,"text":"Yeah? I would actually prefer to do it more this way."},{"time":684000,"text":"Some people would make apple pie out of it."},{"time":688000,"text":"But it's a very good example to see that the whole work"},{"time":690000,"text":"was more of a handicraft endeavor that involved the very time-consuming job"},{"time":695000,"text":"of cutting out the various elements and sticking them back in new arrangements."},{"time":701000,"text":"And it's not done, as many people imagine, with the computer,"},{"time":704000,"text":"otherwise it would look like this."},{"time":708000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":713000,"text":"So now I've been able to tidy up pictures that I've wanted to tidy up for a long time."},{"time":719000,"text":"Here is a very good example. Take Jackson Pollock, for example."},{"time":722000,"text":"It's -- oh, no, it's -- that's a really hard one."},{"time":727000,"text":"But after a while, I just decided here to go all the way"},{"time":732000,"text":"and put the paint back into the cans."},{"time":735000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":745000,"text":"Or you could go into three-dimensional art."},{"time":750000,"text":"Here we have the fur cup by Meret Oppenheim."},{"time":755000,"text":"Here I just brought it back to its original state."},{"time":758000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":766000,"text":"But yeah, and it's great, you can even go, you know --"},{"time":771000,"text":"Or we have this pointillist movement for those of you who are into art."},{"time":777000,"text":"The pointillist movement is that kind of paintings"},{"time":780000,"text":"where everything is broken down into dots and pixels."},{"time":783000,"text":"And then I -- this sort of thing is ideal for tidying up."},{"time":787000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":790000,"text":"So I once applied myself to the work of the inventor of that method, Georges Seurat,"},{"time":794000,"text":"and I collected together all his dots."},{"time":796000,"text":"And now they're all in here."},{"time":798000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":803000,"text":"You can count them afterwards, if you like."},{"time":804000,"text":"You see, that's the wonderful thing about the tidy up art idea:"},{"time":809000,"text":"it's new. So there is no existing tradition in it."},{"time":812000,"text":"There is no textbooks, I mean, not yet, anyway."},{"time":816000,"text":"I mean, it's \"the future we will create.\""},{"time":820000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":822000,"text":"But to round things up I would like to show you just one more."},{"time":827000,"text":"This is the village square by Pieter Bruegel."},{"time":830000,"text":"That's how it looks like when you send everyone home."},{"time":833000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":844000,"text":"Yeah, maybe you're asking yourselves"},{"time":846000,"text":"where old Bruegel's people went?"},{"time":850000,"text":"Of course, they're not gone. They're all here."},{"time":854000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":855000,"text":"I just piled them up."},{"time":857000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":861000,"text":"So I'm -- yeah, actually I'm kind of finished at that moment."},{"time":865000,"text":"And for those who want to see more, I've got my book downstairs in the bookshop."},{"time":871000,"text":"And I'm happy to sign it for you with any name of any artist."},{"time":876000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":878000,"text":"But before leaving I would like to show you,"},{"time":882000,"text":"I'm working right now on another -- in a related field"},{"time":887000,"text":"with my tidying up art method. I'm working in a related field."},{"time":890000,"text":"And I started to bring some order into some flags."},{"time":896000,"text":"Here -- that's just my new proposal here for the Union Jack."},{"time":903000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":908000,"text":"And then maybe before I leave you ..."},{"time":913000,"text":"yeah, I think, after you have seen that I have to leave anyway."},{"time":917000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":920000,"text":"Yeah, that was a hard one. I couldn't find a way to tidy that up properly,"},{"time":926000,"text":"so I just decided to make it a little bit more simpler."},{"time":930000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":932000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":933000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}